    <h1>LIBRARY</h1>
<h2>LIBRARY</h2>
<p>The central Library (area: 10000 Sq.ft) has extensive collections of books and is augmented on a continuous basis. The Library subscribes to numerous numbers of popular periodicals, National and International Journals, CD ROM’s are also available. As of now it has more than 40000 books and journals.

The approximate annual addition is about 2500 volumes. 160 periodicals including 2000 international journals are being subscribed in our Library.

It is a most lively place on the campus providing a safe, comfortable and friendly environment that enables learning and advancement of knowledge, and promotes discovery and scholarship.
    </p>
    
