    <h2>MISSION</h2>
<p>To facilitate creation of new knowledge through acquisition, organization and dissemination of knowledge resources and providing for value added services.
    </p>

<h2>LIBRARY SERVICES</h2>
<p>PJCE Library is providing wide and varied services to support strongly for the learning and teaching process.

Circulation (i.e. issue and return of books) takes place through Barcode System. All details of the Library collections are fed into the Computer and provide Online Public Access Catalogue (OPAC) to our users. Our college Library is well equipped with computing facilities and Audio Visual aids.
    </p>
<h2>TUTORIAL FOR E-RESOURCES</h2>
<p>For the effective use of the library facilities and e-resources, a detailed tutorial to access e-resources; which explains step-by-step procedure to access e- Journals has been prepared and circulated to all the faculty members and students.
